<h2 style="font-family:verdana; color:#333">10s Number Bracelet</h2>

<div style="line-height:2">
<p style="font-family:verdana; color:#333">10s Number Bracelet contains five red beads and five white beads. The two coloured beads enable children to subitize quantity easier. To split the beads into left and right, click on the beads. Use this visual tool to demonstrate the 11 ways to make 10. Click<img src="https://alfaandfriends.com/maths-digitaltools/00-icons/ui_visibility.png" width="40" height="40" style="vertical-align:middle">to make the number pairs to make 10 visible and not visible to children. You will notice that the boxes containing the numbers next to the 10s Number Bracelet disappear or appear.</p>
</div>